# Unify Lark Webhook Settings and Improve Visibility

The user is unable to find the Lark test feature. My research shows that the test functionality is present in the [WebhookSettingsModal](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/WebhookSettingsModal.tsx#26-306) (used in [DailyMeetingView](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#2531-2988)) and on the `/sandbox` page, but the [Home](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/app/page.tsx#47-435) page uses an older, inline webhook settings UI that lacks the "Run Test" button.

