1. Open the application.
2. Click the "Members" button in the header.
3. Verify that the [WebhookSettingsModal](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/WebhookSettingsModal.tsx#26-306) opens and contains the "Run Test" section.
